mari0 for Debian
----------------

Currently love-unstable (which is required to run this game) is only available
via the ppa at: https://launchpad.net/~bartbes/+archive/love-unstable

You can add that ppa to your apt sources with the command sudo
add-apt-repository ppa:bartbes/love-unstable

